<!-- Beginning of Section 6 - Benefits and values of the company -->

<div class="section-6-background">
  <div class="section-6">
    <h4 class="centered blue-text">Benefits and company culture</h4>
    <h5 class="centered">Our search paramaters include to:</h5>
    <br>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">

        <div class="small-icon-resized benefit-title">
          <div class="mr-3"><%=image_tag("success.png") %></div>
          <div><h6>Define the benefits that are important to you</h6></div>

        </div>

        <p class="small-text">Filter your research from a multitude of benefits that are important to you, as equity, 30+ days of parental leave, beach within 60 minutes, professional development budget, and much more!</p>

      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">

        <div class="small-icon-resized benefit-title">
          <div class="mr-3"><%=image_tag("money.png")%></div>

          <div><h6>Filter the results by your salary expectations</h6></div>
        </div>
        <p class="small-text">Don't waste your time and decide to see the job opportunities only if they meet your minimum salary requirement.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">

        <div class="small-icon-resized benefit-title">
          <div class="mr-3"><%=image_tag("share.png")%></div>

          <div><h6>Connect your professional networks in a few seconds</h6></div>
        </div>
        <p class="small-text">Make your profile more impactful by adding the links to your professionnal networks directly on your personal page, such as LinkedIn and GitHub.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">

        <div class="small-icon-resized benefit-title">
          <div class="mr-3"><%=image_tag("pin.png")%></div>

          <div><h6>Set a perimeter of research... or decide to be remote!</h6></div>
        </div>
        <p class="small-text">Filter your job search by one or multiple locations, and/or choose to look for a remote job.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">

        <div class="small-icon-resized benefit-title">
          <div class="mr-3"><%=image_tag("star.png")%></div>

          <div><h6>Shape your profile with your skills and competencies</h6></div>
        </div>
        <p class="small-text">Add your skills with your level of proficiency, and precise your experiences.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">

        <div class="small-icon-resized benefit-title">
          <div class="mr-3"><%=image_tag("view.png")%></div>

          <div><h6>Have an in-depth look to the companies values</h6></div>
        </div>
        <p class="small-text">Before applying to a job, you now have an overview of the company's values, expectations and way to work.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <% if current_user %>
  <div class="bottom-padding-home"></div>
  <% else %>
  <div class="centered">
